Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.28,0:00:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahbmad!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.28,0:00:18.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（アリババ）アブマド！\N俺は　お前と　この国の現状に→
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.74,0:00:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I have come to put an end to the status quo in this country!
