Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.21,0:22:19.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ？　アラジン　まさか…。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.27,0:22:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Aladdin! He couldn't have-!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.82,0:22:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.82,0:22:25.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（武器商人）来たか。　さあ　運命よ→
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.74,0:22:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Swing, pendulum.
